if you were the one to do it!

18:59.580 --> 19:02.720
I want him to defeat the Devil King!

19:02.720 --> 19:05.580
I ask you to stop and you start 
spamming the Elder Brother button?!

19:05.580 --> 19:07.730
Are you trying to pick a fight!

19:07.730 --> 19:09.180
D-Do you want one?!

19:09.180 --> 19:11.480
R-Royals are strong, you know!

19:11.480 --> 19:12.910
How dare you?!

19:11.480 --> 19:12.910
