19:19.340 --> 19:21.640
My Exterion is strong, too, y'know!

19:19.860 --> 19:22.560
You've never been in a fight before!

19:24.330 --> 19:27.660
So... what was it you wanted to ask?

19:27.660 --> 19:29.250
Anything you want.

19:31.340 --> 19:34.780
Right... I wanted to ask you...

19:43.150 --> 19:45.860
We still haven't settled our game.

19:46.260 --> 19:49.820
I'd love for you to come and play me again.

19:59.380 --> 19:59.940
KO!

19:59.940 --> 20:00.480
NO!

20:00.480 --> 20:00.990
SU!

20:00.990 --> 20:01.380
BA!

20:05.370 --> 20:07.220
Would you quiet down?

20:07.220 --> 20:10.260
You're being a disturbance. If you want 
to shout, do it outside of town.

20:10.260 --> 20:12.810
Screw you! Just when things 
were going so well!

20:12.620 --> 20:16.240
Next time... if I could 
get your autograph...

20:12.810 --> 20:16.240
When you said all that crap 
about fighting the Devil King,

20:16.240 --> 20:18.660
