wanted me to stay with her,

20:20.400 --> 20:21.970
or that she wanted to go out with me,

20:21.970 --> 20:23.900
or that she wanted to sleep in my bed!

20:23.900 --> 20:26.180
You're being ridiculous.

20:26.180 --> 20:28.950
Do you actually believe you're capable

20:28.950 --> 20:32.180
of convincing someone to 
fall for you in only a week?

20:32.180 --> 20:34.150
Face reality.

20:34.150 --> 20:36.790
Don't drag me back there!

20:36.790 --> 20:39.420
I don't wanna be fact-checked!

20:41.450 --> 20:45.920
Just... let me dream a little more.

20:46.420 --> 20:49.440
I can't believe the thieves 
took your precious ring...

20:49.900 --> 20:52.260
We will accept any punishment you see fit.

20:52.830 --> 20:55.950
You two did everything you could.

20:55.950 --> 20:58.270
Please, don't be so upset.

20:58.810 --> 21:00.600
We are grateful for your mercy.

21:06.740 --> 21:09.580
<i>That ring has a certain 
rule associated with it.</i>

21:10.020 --> 21:13.030
<i>Whoever slays the Devil King, as a reward,</i>

21:13.520 --> 21:17.760
<i>will gain the right to take 
the princess as their bride.</i>

21:19.080 --> 21:20.600
<i>Big Brother...</i>

21:22.430 --> 21:26.090
<i>I hope he takes good care of the ring.</i>

22:59.600 --> 23:01.010
My Divine Treasure...

23:01.350 --> 23:04.930
Not only did the thief 
steal my Divine Treasure,

23:04.930 --> 23:06.640
but they've sealed it away, too?!

23:07.020 --> 23:08.900
Find it!

23:09.270 --> 23:11.440
I can't...

23:11.440 --> 23:16.150
If the Divine Treasure's been sealed, 
there's nothing I can do...

23:16.620 --> 23:19.410
You useless wretch!

23:19.410 --> 23:24.120
When are you going to 
actually grant my wish?!

